<template><div><h1 id="expand-tilde" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#expand-tilde" aria-hidden="true">#</a> expand-tilde <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/expand-tilde" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/v/expand-tilde.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM version"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://npmjs.org/package/expand-tilde" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/npm/dm/expand-tilde.svg?style=flat" alt="NPM downloads"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> <a href="https://travis-ci.org/jonschlinkert/expand-tilde" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://img.shields.io/travis/jonschlinkert/expand-tilde.svg?style=flat&amp;label=Travis" alt="Linux Build Status"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h1>
<blockquote>
<p>Bash-like tilde expansion for node.js. Expands a leading tilde in a file path to the user home directory, or <code v-pre>~+</code> to the cwd.</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="install" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#install" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Install</h2>
<p>Install with <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">npm<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>:</p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> --save expand-tilde
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="usage" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#usage" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Usage</h2>
<p>See the <a href="https://www.gnu.org/software/bash/manual/html_node/Tilde-Expansion.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bash documentation for Tilde Expansion<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>.</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">var</span> expandTilde <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">require</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'expand-tilde'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

<span class="token function">expandTilde</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'~'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">//=> '/Users/jonschlinkert'</span>

<span class="token function">expandTilde</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'~+'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">//=> process.cwd()</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="run-tests" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#run-tests" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Run tests</h2>
